- `./src/components` - Client-side components (React islands and wrappers)
- `./src/components/ui` - Shadcn/ui base components
- `./src/components/{feature}` - Feature-specific components (e.g., dashboard, transactions)
- `./src/hooks` - React hooks for data fetching and state management
- `./src/lib` - Services, API clients, and utilities
- `./src/lib/api` - API client functions
- `./src/lib/services` - Business logic services
- `./src/lib/utils` - Shared utility functions
